For example:

			&lt;plugin&gt;
				&lt;groupId&gt;org.apache.maven.plugins&lt;/groupId&gt;
				&lt;artifactId&gt;maven-javadoc-plugin&lt;/artifactId&gt;
				&lt;version&gt;3.3.2&lt;/version&gt;
				&lt;configuration&gt;
					&lt;sourcepath&gt;src/main/java;${defines.dir}&lt;/sourcepath&gt;
